des: Welcome to FNTSY Sports Radio Network, where you can get your free fantasy fix 24 hours a day, seven days a week, from the FNTSY Sports Network. Season long, daily fantasy (DFS), weird pools and formats -- it doesn't matter. We give you tips, strategy, and advice that is produced, hosted and over-analyzed by your favorite fantasy personalities. In short, we're here to help you win. Want to participate? Call in at (844) 843-6879 that's (844) 84 FNTSY. Listen for FREE, dominate your league, and thank us later. The FNTSY Sports Radio Network. You bring your ears, we'll bring our "A" game.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
